<p><img  src="http://www.dur.ac.uk/butler.jcr/application/views/involved/img/upload/005.jpg" alt="" width="314" height="309" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span ><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >Who Are We?</span></span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >Josephine Butler College Choir is a friendly choir of about thirty singers. </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >There's NO AUDITION and you don&rsquo;t have to be able to read music, but you&rsquo;ll learn as we work our way through the music. Rehearsals provide a welcome break from work, a chance to meetup and have a sing&nbsp;with friends and a way to gain confidence and improve your musical ability.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >What&rsquo;s On? </span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >IN ADDITION to the college and uni events and traditional Christmas Carol singing,&nbsp;we are planning on singing&nbsp;an Evensong in Durham Cathedral the 24th</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" > of February and a springtime concert in college.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >With at least two concerts a term, spanning as wide a range of choral music as possible, there's bound to be SOMETHING FOR EVERYBODY! And most importantly, we are going to have socials and loads of fun!</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >Get Involved! </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span class="Apple-style-span" ><span class="Apple-style-span" >We rehearse from 7.30-9pm every&nbsp;THURSDAY in the HOWLANDS MUSIC ROOM. SEE YOU THERE :D x</span></span></span></p><p><span ><span >&nbsp;</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>